text: Courtney King-Dye (born November 20, 1977) is an American equestrian. She competed in two events at the 2008 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:American female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the United States Category:Equestrians at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saginaw, Michigan
